author: akarasulu
msg: Injected the ResultResponse which has a LDAPResult component according to
RFC2251.  Made the mistake that all responses have the LdapResult component
however it turns out that only the BindResponse, SearchResultDone,
and ExtendedResponse messages have the LdapResult component. The other
responses SearchResEntry, SearchResRef and Abandon do not have the
LDAPResult component and therefore derive from the Response interface
